Text: ...Okay, we're here. She's inside this room.

"Photography Club"...? That doesn't sound like it
would have anything to do with the making of
Darkollector.
...And even worse, it's THAT photo club.
You know this club, Zeta?
You'll see for yourself. Anyway, in we go. Excuse us!
Oh, wait—

No one's here, even though the door was unlocked.
Did she go somewhere?
No, she's here. See, over there.
Ugh... Pipe down...
Is that blanket moving...?
Mmf... Who's there?
It's me.
Nuru...

Remember how I said there were some people I wanted
you to meet? Well, I brought them here.
*yawn*... Oh...

Her name's Eta. She's a crazy skilled scientist
who's good at IT or whatever.
...So did you really make Darkollector?

Yeah... But for various reasons...I plan to change
it to "Dark X" soon...

Wow, so there's gonna be an update. Maybe there'll
be some new features?
So...? Why did you want to meet me...?
Wait, you don't know? Nuru, didn't you tell her?

I tried to, but she fell asleep. I did at least
manage to get her to promise, though.

Okay, so we're going to have to start from the
beginning, like who we are and what's happened
so far—

...Um, Eta? Are you awake? I've told you pretty much
everything now, but...
...I'm awake.... I think I get the general idea...

And since I run Darkollector, I'd kinda been keeping
tabs on what you've been up to...
That will make this easy. We want you to join—
No.
...Can you at least let me finish?
Even if I did, my answer would be the same...
*sigh*... I knew it was gonna go this way.

But it's not that you aren't interested, right?
I mean, you DID make Darkollector with Nuru,
after all.

Yes, I made Darkollector... And I am involved in
collecting Bones...

But...all of that is just for my research on the
Dark Histories...

Working with anyone else would just be annoying...
I don't want anyone slowing me down…
But—
Hmm... Welp, guess that's just the way it is.
Zeta?

Hey, we're not trying to force anyone here, so all
we can do is face the facts and head home.

(What's gotten into her? I can't believe she's just
giving up so easily...)
C'mon, Alpha, that means you too.
...O-Okay.
Bye-bye...

...Oh, almost forgot. Totally different topic here,
but—

I heard the Photography Club is in danger of being
shut down.
Urk...
Shut down?

You didn't hear, Alpha? The student council has made
announcements about it plenty of times.
...How do you know that?

Because the Photography Club is famous, why else?
...Oh, but I mean that in a bad way.

There's rumors that the club took apart all the fire
alarms in school, and then to top it off, tried to
build an underground shelter beneath campus.
Crazy stuff like that.

And then there's the fact that you're the only
member. In other words you don't even meet
the minimum number of people to be a club.
No wonder it's on the verge of getting axed.

I mean, from the beginning, you've only been using
this club and room however you want, anyway.

...I haven't done anything wrong. Students have the
right to use school equipment.

It's all the student council president's fault for
being such a stickler about the budget. She's...
just trying to find an excuse to shut the club
down...

(After hearing all that, it sounds like she kind of
had it coming...)

You can talk all the trash you want, but it's true
you're almost done for, right? Word is the student
council is about to get serious about disbanding
your little club.
Grr...

Bad behavior is one thing, but not having enough
members really is bad. That can be used as clear
grounds for disbanding the club. How many people
do you need minimum?
...Four. So three more...

But you can't get those three members on your own,
huh? Otherwise you'd already have them.
...So, how about we recruit some members for you?
...Are you...trying to bargain with me?

You get to keep your club going, and we get more
allies. Doesn't sound like a bad deal to me!
Nngh...
...Got it. So, if you find three people...I'll join you.

Heehee, it's a deal, then. Now, just relax and leave
the rest to us.

Relax...? We still need one more person besides us,
no? What's your plan?

Guess we'll just have to come up with something,
huh.

That's so sloppy... This has a big effect on me,
too, you know. Do you get that?

Alright, alright, that's enough scolding. We need to
find a good candidate for our last memb—

...Hold up a sec. Those footsteps approaching
needlessly fast... Could it be...her?
C'mon out!!! I know you're in there, Zeta!
